256
00:36:23,599 --> 00:36:28,204
Looks like you have no faith
in the police force.

257
00:36:28,566 --> 00:36:33,537
That's not true. It's just
that Anand is not around and...

258
00:36:34,666 --> 00:36:35,633
l understand.

259
00:36:39,466 --> 00:36:43,236
