Do you want to kidnap her?

269
00:38:40,966 --> 00:38:43,802
Nandita Rai...
isn't that your name?

270
00:38:46,033 --> 00:38:48,502
Who the hell are you?

271
00:38:50,466 --> 00:38:52,367
l'm her mother.

272
00:38:54,400 --> 00:38:56,168
Neha is my daughter.

273
00:39:06,500 --> 00:39:09,269
Your daughter...?!
- Yes.

274
00:39:11,233 --> 00:39:16,204
l have borne the child
you are mother to.

275
00:39:39,833 --> 00:39:41,601
Give it another thought, Kavita.

276
00:39:42,566 --> 00:39:45,669
l don't really need a child.
l can live with your support.

277
00:39:46,066 --> 00:39:51,671
l know. l've drawn strength from
your love to take this decision.

278
00:40:06,199 --> 00:40:07,968
When will she start walking?

279
00:40:08,500 --> 00:40:13,471
She's just a week old.
- My friend's in a hury.

280
00:40:13,833 --> 00:40:17,870
You'd better give the baby the
car-keys. She'll drive us home!

281
00:40:28,033 --> 00:40:35,507
l haven't come to take Neha back.
She belongs to you. And always will.

282
00:40:37,400 --> 00:40:41,070
lt's just that l came to
take a look at her.

283
00:40:45,166 --> 00:40:48,702
l'm sory. l've caused you
a lot of inconvenience.

284
00:40:48,966 --> 00:40:52,302
