292
00:41:35,833 --> 00:41:39,570
Perhaps it was my feeling of
motherhood, perhaps selfishness.

293
00:41:41,166 --> 00:41:43,001
Or the sense of belonging.

294
00:41:45,366 --> 00:41:50,537
Do not wory. l will go away
as suddenly as l came.

295
00:42:00,866 --> 00:42:02,901
When Neha grows up,...

296
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:07,270
she might not even remember
having met someone like me.

297
00:42:10,566 --> 00:42:12,034
