one last time.

302
00:42:39,466 --> 00:42:42,435
l've been so rude to you.

303
00:42:44,366 --> 00:42:47,535
l liked whatever you said.

304
00:42:48,966 --> 00:42:53,236
Neha's lucky to have found
a mother like you.

305
00:42:55,533 --> 00:42:58,135
But she loves her papa more.

306
00:42:58,666 --> 00:43:02,002
He must be better than you then.
- l think so too.

307
00:43:05,266 --> 00:43:05,266
Let's take auntie home.
l'll show her all my toys!

308
00:43:08,699 --> 00:43:13,671
You invite her, dear.
- Some other day, okay?

309
00:43:14,766 --> 00:43:17,735
No! Come with us right now!
We live close-by.

310
00:43:17,900 --> 00:43:22,871
