Anything else?

337
00:45:35,699 --> 00:45:40,671
l'll see you in the evening tomorrow.
It's my day off, you know.

338
00:45:45,866 --> 00:45:47,767
What will you have?
- Black coffee.

339
00:45:49,066 --> 00:45:53,537
l forgot to introduce you to Somu.
- l already know him.

340
00:45:53,733 --> 00:45:58,704
Do you really know me?
- Yes. Neha told me evemhing.

341
00:45:59,800 --> 00:46:02,135
But there's something
l didn't tell you.

342
00:46:03,733 --> 00:46:06,902
l just can't understand
his poety!

343
00:46:08,366 --> 00:46:11,535
Where are you put up, Nandita?
- At the Radisson.

344
00:46:13,966 --> 00:46:16,702
