Let's play a computer game, auntie!

354
00:46:59,300 --> 00:47:00,567
- Sure.

355
00:47:05,933 --> 00:47:10,904
lsn't it strange?
Neha hardly knows Nandita...

356
00:47:11,800 --> 00:47:13,635
but she's so comfortable

357
00:47:19,199 --> 00:47:20,935
She's her mother, Somu.

358
00:47:22,866 --> 00:47:25,201
The two ofyou have
gone crazy!

359
00:47:25,300 --> 00:47:28,770
