adoption laws!

361
00:47:30,933 --> 00:47:34,036
l wouldn't know about all that.
Ask her whatever you want to.

362
00:47:45,966 --> 00:47:49,202
l'll be back soon.
- Where are you going?

363
00:47:49,366 --> 00:47:51,468
To the Raddisson.
To pick up Nandita's luggage.

364
00:47:52,466 --> 00:47:56,002
ls she here then?
- Yes. They're waiting for you.

365
00:48:06,833 --> 00:48:09,569
What was Somu talking about?
Why did you allow her to stay here?

366
00:48:09,666 --> 00:48:12,402
Why don't you meet her, Anand?
- Why must l?

367
00:48:12,466 --> 00:48:15,735
How do you know what she wants?
l think she's an impostor!

368
00:48:15,833 --> 00:48:17,234
Where is she?
And where is Neha?

369
00:48:25,266 --> 00:48:30,104
Wash your hands, dim girl!
Hury up!

370
00:49:18,099 --> 00:49:19,701
Help!

371
00:49:32,900 --> 00:49:34,134
Leave her alone!

372
00:50:26,066 --> 00:50:27,167
Rip him apart!

373
00:53:02,633 --> 00:53:05,168
Let me make your plaits!
- No!

374
00:53:10,866 --> 00:53:10,866
Sit down! Or l'll have
your hair cut short!

375
00:53:13,766 --> 00:53:18,036
No way! Auntie says
l have vey nice hair.

376
00:53:22,500 --> 00:53:25,269
Here l am.
Your check-out is over.

377
00:53:26,366 --> 00:53:29,969
