- Let her finish her breakfast!

407
00:56:52,366 --> 00:56:55,635
What's up?
- Nothing at all.

408
00:56:56,000 --> 00:56:57,901
Don't lie. You get caught.

409
00:56:58,800 --> 00:57:01,569
You haven't even looked at me
since you've arrived.

410
00:57:06,866 --> 00:57:09,835
Were you taken aback
to see Nandita here?

411
00:57:11,166 --> 00:57:16,838
Strange ironies of life.
l wonder how she feels.

412
00:57:20,166 --> 00:57:25,137
Has she given you her address?
- She doesn't want to.

413
00:57:25,233 --> 00:57:28,970
She said she's happy to see Neha
here and won't come back again.

414
00:57:33,033 --> 00:57:35,869
You're attending the meeting
with Mr Bansal, aren't you, sir?

415
00:57:36,033 --> 00:57:37,934
l told you l'd be late.

416
00:57:38,466 --> 00:57:40,734
Ask them to leave,
ifthey can't wait!

417
00:57:49,033 --> 00:57:53,003
What's wrong?
You're okay, aren't you?

418
00:57:57,000 --> 00:57:57,834
Tired?

419
00:58:00,166 --> 00:58:04,069
You didn't like my allowing
her to stay here, did you?

420
00:58:04,766 --> 00:58:08,369
She's leaving, Anand.
And l wanted you to meet her once.

421
00:58:11,333 --> 00:58:14,002
All right. l'll dress up
and come downstairs.

422
00:58:16,966 --> 00:58:20,002
l could drop her at the station
on my way to the office.

423
00:58:20,966 --> 00:58:24,302
Okay. But don't ask her
awkward questions.

424
00:58:24,566 --> 00:58:27,035
l don't know what she's
is going through.

425
00:58:29,366 --> 00:58:33,036
You stay away for so many days...
don't you ever miss me?

426
00:58:35,033 --> 00:58:36,267
Liar!

427
00:58:48,233 --> 00:58:52,236
That's the number.
Make an enquiy again.

428
00:58:52,866 --> 00:58:55,168
