442
00:59:59,300 --> 01:00:00,534
l'm leaving for the office.

443
01:00:06,366 --> 01:00:07,767
Aren't you forgetting something?

444
01:00:21,300 --> 01:00:25,470
What a coincidence! l gave Kavita
the first copy ofthis edition...

445
01:00:26,000 --> 01:00:28,969
and l'm giRing to you
the last copy!

446
01:00:29,566 --> 01:00:31,467
We have another copy, sir.

447
01:00:36,066 --> 01:00:38,301
For you.

448
01:00:38,933 --> 01:00:40,968
When is your next book arriving?
- Soon.

449
01:00:41,800 --> 01:00:46,771
Have you read ''Dil Kya Kare'' ?
- Sure. Your love-poems are great.

450
01:01:16,166 --> 01:01:17,433
You?

451
01:01:19,033 --> 01:01:26,373
Sory... did l startle you?
- No. l expected to meet you here.

452
01:01:27,666 --> 01:01:29,134
Please sit down.

453
01:01:48,199 --> 01:01:50,669
Without sugar.
- The same for me.

454
01:02:00,066 --> 01:02:00,966
l don't know...

455
01:02:02,900 --> 01:02:04,501
where to begin from.

456
01:02:09,466 --> 01:02:13,870
Forgive me for lying
about the train.

457
01:02:14,900 --> 01:02:19,004
l had so many questions to ask,
when l saw you again.

458
01:02:19,766 --> 01:02:21,601
l wanted to talk to you too.

459
01:02:24,566 --> 01:02:31,673
